Uhlelo lokusebenza ludinga isibuyekezo samasevisi we-Google Play.
Uhlelo lokusebenza ludinga ukubuyekezelwa kuhlelo lokusebenza le-Android Wear.
Uhlelo lokusebenza ludinga amasevisi we-Google Play ukuze anikwe amandla.
Lolu hlelo lokusebenza ngeke lusebenze ngaphandle kwamasevisi e-Google Play, angekho efonini yakho.
Lolu hlelo lokusebenza ngeke lusebenze ngaphandle kwamasevisi e-Google Play, angekho kuthebulethi yakho.
Lolu hlelo lokusebenza ngeke lusebenze ngaphandle nje kokuthi unike amandla amasevisi e-Google Play.
Lolu hlelo lokusebenza ngeke lusebenze ngaphandle nje kokuthi ubuyekeze amasevisi e-Google Play.
Lolu hlelo lokusebenza ngeke lusebenze ngaphandle kokuthi ubuyekeze uhlelo lokusebenza le-Android Wear.
Kudingeka ukuxhumeka kwedatha ukuze kuxhunyekwe kumasevisi we-Google Play.
I-Akhawunti ecacisiwe ayikho kule divayisi. Sicela ukhethe i-akhawunti ehlukile.
Amasevisi we-Google Play, okungukuthi ezinye izinhlelo zakho zithembele kuwo, awasekelwe yidivayisi yakho. Sicela uxhumane nomkhiqizi ukuze uthole usizo.
Lawa masevisi enza i-Google ikusebenzele, futhi ungawavula uphinde uwavale noma kunini. Idatha izosetshenziswa ngokuhambisana ne-Inqubomgomo Yobumfihlo ye-Google.

Yenza isipele izinhlelo zokusebenza zefoni yakho, idatha yohlelo lokusebenza, izilungiselelo, izichazamazwi zokomuntu siqu, namaphasiwedi we-Wi-Fi usebenzisa i-akhawunti yakho ye-Google ukuze ukwazi ukubuyisela kalula ngemva kwesikhathi. Funda kabanzi

Yenza isipele izinhlelo zakho zokusebenza, idatha yohlelo lokusebenza, izilungiselelo, izichazamazwi zokomuntu siqu, namaphasiwedi we-Wi-Fi usebenzisa i-akhawunti yakho ye-Google ukuze ukwazi ukubuyisela kalula ngemva kwesikhathi.
Idatha ifaka izinhlelo zokusebenza, izilungiselelo zohlelo lokusebenza, izilungiselelo zesistimu, namaphasiwedi we-Wi-Fi.

Uma uvula ukwenza isipele ngokuzenzakalelayo, idatha yedivayisi yakho ilondolozwa ngesikhathi ku-Akhawunti yakho ye-Google. Izipele zingafaka phakathi ulwazi kumafolda wakho wedatha yohlelo lokusebenza, njengezintandokazi, izilungiselelo, imilayezo, izithombe namanye amafayela.

Sebenzisa isevisi yendawo ye-Google ukuze usize izinhlelo zokusebenza zicacise indawo. Lokhu kusho ukuthumela idatha yendawo ngokungaziwa ku-Google, ngosho noma ngabe azikho izinhlelo zokusebenza ezisebenzayo. Funda kabanzi

Isevisi yendawo ye-Google isebenzisa imithombo efana ne-Wi‑Fi namanethiwekhi weselula ukusiza ukucabangela indawo yedivayisi yakho ngokushesha nokuqonda kakhulu. Uma uvula amasevisi wendawo we-Google, idivayisi yakho ingena imodi esebenzisa i-Wi‑Fi namanethiwekhi weselula ukunikeza ngolwazi lendawo. Ingavala lokhu kuzilungiselelo zendawo ngokukhetha imodi esebenzisa i-GPS kuphela, kwesinye isikhathi ibizwa nge-Imodi yedivayisi kuphela.
Siza ukuthuthukisa amasevisi wendawo ngokuvumela izinhlelo zokusebenza namasevisi ukuthi askene amanethiwekhi we-Wi‑Fi ngisho noma i-Wi‑Fi ivaliwe.

Isevisi yendawo ye-Google isebenzisa i-Wi-Fi namanye amasiginali ukuze inqume indawo ngokuqondile kakhulu nangokushesha, ngokuvamisile ngokusetshenziswa kwamandla okuphansi kune-GPS. Enye idatha ingalondolozwa kudivayisi yakho. Idatha ingaqoqwa noma ngabe kungekho izinhlelo zokusebenza ezisebenzayo.
Hlala ungazisa nezindaba nokunikezwayo kusuka ku-Google Play.

Siza ukuthuthukisa umuzwa wakho we-Android ngokuthumela ngokuzenzakalelayo idatha yokuthola nokusebenzisa ku-Google. Lolu lwazi ngeke lusetshenziswe ukukukhomba futhi lunikezwe kumathimba asebenza ngezinto ezifana nempilo yebhethri, ukusebenza kwezinhlelo zokusebenza, nezici ezintsha ze-Google. Funa kabanzi

"Lolu ulwazi oluvamile mayelana nedivayisi yakho nokuthi uyisebenzisa kanjani, njengeleveli yebhethri, ukuthi uzisebenzisa kanjani izinhlelo zakho zokusebenza, ikhwalithi nokuqina koxhumo lwakho lenethiwekhi (njengeseli, i-Wi‑Fi, ne-Bluetooth), nemibiko yokusaphazeka uma izinto zingasebenzi ngendlela efanele. Luzosetshenziselwa ukuthuthukisa imikhiqizo ye-Google namasevisi kuwo wonke umuntu, futhi ngeke luphathelaniswe ne-Akhawunti yakho ye-Google. Olunye ulwazi oluhlanganisiwe luzosiza ozakwethu, njengonjiniyela be-Android, benze izinhlelo zabo zokusebenza nemikhiqizo ibengcono, futhi.
Ungavula noma uvale lokhu noma kunini kuhlelo lokuseenza lezilungiselelo ze-Google. Lokhu akuthinti amandla wedivayisi yakho ukuthumela ulwazi oluludingatho ukuthola amasevisi abalulekile njengezibuyekezo zesistimu nokuvikeleka."

Le foni futhi ingathola futhi ifake izibuyekezo nezinhlelo zokusebenza kusuka ku-Google, inkampani yakho yenethiwekhi, nomkhiqizi wefoni yakho. Ezinye izinhlelo zokusebenza zingahle zilandwe futhi zifakwe uma uqhubeka, futhi ungazisusa noma kunini.

Ikhansela ukwenza kusebenze... lokhu kungase kuthathe amasekhondi angu-5-10.

Kube nephutha elidinga ukucinywa nokuqala kabusha kocingo lakho ngaphambi kokwenza omunye umzamo wokusebenzisa. Ucingo lakho lizocima ngokuzenzakalela emasekhondini angu-60, noma ungathinta u-Cima manje".
Uma ucingo lakho selicimile, cindezela inkinobho yamandla. Ukusebenza ukuzoqala ngokuzenzakalela."

Le foni futhi ithola izibuyekezo ezisheshayo kusuk ku-Google. Ngokuqhubeka, uyavumelana nemigomo yesevisi ye-Google nenqubomgomo yokwemfihlo.

Uvumelana ngokuthuthukile ukuthi idivayisi yakho ingathola futhi ifake izibuyekezo kusuka ku-Google. Uma usebenzisa le divayisi sibophezelekile nge-Inqubomgomo Yokwefihlo nemigomo engeziwe iyasebenza.
Ifoni yakho ilungiselelwe ukusebenza futhi ikulungele ukusetshenziswa.
Qala i-Verizon Backup Assistant ukubuyisa oxhumana nabo kusuka kolunye ucingo le-Verizon.

Uzoqondiswa ukuze usethe ukukhiya isikrini kwakho uma ukhetha uyebo.
Vikela le divayisi uphinde ufune i-PIN, iphethini, noma iphasiwedi ukuze uvule isikrini

"Ukuvikela idivayisi kwenziwa kusebenze ngokuzenzakalela uma ungeza i-Akhawunti ye-Google uphinde usetha ukukhiya isikrini. Ngokuhambisana ne-Isiphathi Sedivayisi ye-Android, ungathola indawo uphinde usule ifoni yakho, uphinde uyivikele kusukela ekusetshenzisweni futhi uma ilahleka noma intshontshwa.
Noma ngabe ifoni yakho isulwa, iphasiwedi yakho ye-Akhawunti ye-Google izodingeka ngaphambi kokuthi noma ubani asebenzise le foni."
Izici zokuvikela idivayisi ngeke zenziwe zisebenze. Ngeke uze ukwazi ukuvimbela abanye kusukela ekusebenziseni le foni uma ilahleka, intshontshwa noma isulwa.
